<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head><title>CSS Test: Floats in nowrap context</title>
<link href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css2/visuren.html#float-position" rel="help" />
<link href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=488725" rel="help" />
<link href="mailto:emilio@crisal.io" rel="author" title="Emilio Cobos Álvarez" />
<link href="https://www.mozilla.org" rel="author" title="Mozilla" />
<link href="reference/float-nowrap-3-ref.xht" rel="match" />
<style>
  div {
    width: 10ch;
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  .float {
    float: right;
    width: 5ch;
    height: 5ch;
    background: blue;
  }
  .nowrap {
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
</head><body><div>
  Some
  <span class="nowrap">
    text that overflows <span class="float"></span> my parent.
  </span>
</div>
</body></html>